metadata.description: **Don't miss out! Minting is live here:** ***https://coolcatsnft.art.*** *First time offered: AI-generated Cool Cats oil masterpieces.* Cool Cats are among the most actively traded and valuable NFT collections.  Rare Cats command hundreds of thousands of dollars, and even “floor” cats fetch tens of thousands. Now, for the first time, you can mint spectacular AI-generated oil paintings of the full Cool Cats collection.  Employing over 100 AI technologies, this gorgeous collection allows connoisseurs to enjoy Cool Cats with additional color, texture, and detail like never before.  Mint before they’re gone, then sell, trade, collect, or use however you would like during this era of explosive metaverse growth. Only one minting is available for each of the 9,999 Cool Cats, with every owner receiving an individual ERC-721 token with proof of ownership on the Ethereum blockchain.
